  "keyFeatures": [
    "AprilTag/Fiducial tracking with full 3D pose estimation",
    "MegaTag2 robot localization using gyro-fused pose estimation",
    "Neural network pipeline support (classifier and detector)",
    "Color and retroreflective target tracking",
    "Barcode detection (QR codes, DataMatrix, etc.)",
    "Built-in IMU data access for robot orientation",
    "WPILib Pose2d/Pose3d integration for odometry",
    "NetworkTables-based communication with zero configuration",
    "LED, stream mode, and camera crop control",
    "USB port forwarding for tethered connections"
  ],
